{"tid":1383582,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎睇睇]今日國務院記招有啟示","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:08:51.000Z","uid":280593,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7edb6af78aee385c71fa90a1dd5186171b80a6","tid":1383582,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:17:46.000Z","msg":"中央堅決支持777施政，堅決支持唔代表讚，支持咁多年，個個都出事<br />\n<br />\n話送中唔關中央事，即係話林奠撤回送中ˋ辭職 又或成立獨立調查，中央都會堅決支持<br />\n<br />\n對示威者冇外交部咁強硬，又打開囗牌派糖幫<br />\n<br />\n收左火，即係大家有野做啱左<br />\n<br />\n佢地特别提住三條底褲，而大家ㄧ直係到搞緊(7.1立會、7.7高鐵、721西環)，有理由呢三條底褲係中央死穴<br />\n<br />\n如果想勇武休息下，建議申請高鐵静坐/放映會"},{"pid":"f281a8296f6266dd07d55496c83ccfb21aba5a74","tid":1383582,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"8883ce136b495fc7b55c01114cdf4dff7e317130","tid":1383582,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:47:00.000Z","msg":"希望有心人睇到"},{"pid":"126dd0e695037d4bf0f793a034cb6cc00e05086a","tid":1383582,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"記住 係今天唔出兵 下次會出兵"},{"pid":"0a0899ed0325d911abed6d217c930c86bcf7be83","tid":1383582,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"高鐵放映會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等中共唔比蝗蟲再用高鐵落嚟，睇你要蝕幾多年冷氣，保安錢"},{"pid":"52c047b77202944f8c9994f50efdf80c0de4fa41","tid":1383582,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"126dd0e695037d4bf0f793a034cb6cc00e05086a","tid":1383582,"uid":